    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "मुख्य आर्ग्युमेंट्स:"
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "g/co8j6XUTSclwVVZns62PpdBRMuVyRFZJRSzXDuZE8=",
    "originContent": "Key arguments:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "* `xmis` — डेटा फ्रेम/मैट्रिक्स जिसमें मिसिंग वैल्यूज हों (कॉलम `numeric` या `factor` ही होने चाहिए)।"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "jL/x6Fz0dbzsmypaoAY1cMKOclQnTXk5mz00iRLTBR0=",
    "originContent": "* `xmis` — data frame/matrix with missing values (columns must be `numeric` or `factor`).",
    "translatedContent": "* `maxiter` — अधिकतम इटरेशन (डिफ़ॉल्ट `10`)।"
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "If4SF8hDkP/w8jJC/20wT6h5YhHEMHUn5OTlRa1kI8g=",
    "originContent": "* `maxiter` — maximum iterations (default `10`).",
    "translatedContent": "* `ntree` — प्रत्येक फॉरेस्ट में ट्री की संख्या (डिफ़ॉल्ट `100`)।"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "/PnoHYZsZdrBcpGmg5XS0n+D+WA87UUoUBDu4YCYoI4=",
    "originContent": "* `ntree` — trees per forest (default `100`).",
    "translatedContent": "* `mtry` — प्रत्येक स्प्लिट पर आज़माए जाने वाले वेरिएबल (डिफ़ॉल्ट `sqrt(p)`)।"
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "vIEc4oU9x0t4NR/fYW7LFrY5ur85wqpOnsPjnY1Eop0=",
    "originContent": "* `mtry` — variables tried at each split (default `sqrt(p)`).",
    "translatedContent": "* `nodesize` — **लंबाई-2 न्यूमेरिक**: **c(numeric, factor)** के लिए न्यूनतम नोड साइज। डिफ़ॉल्ट `c(5, 1)`।"
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "ZgNqEzPG2zcB6BOVeG0cTISZDO0KEfML542ouXdJfOs=",
    "originContent": "* `nodesize` — **length-2 numeric**: minimum node size for **c(numeric, factor)**. Default `c(5, 1)`.",
    "translatedContent": "* `variablewise` — यदि `TRUE` तो प्रति-वेरिएबल OOB एरर लौटाता है।"
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "1k0wbRQbQDO8PFknfqJT0L9Hs+Ri1juVktiwwnp+C+8=",
    "originContent": "* `variablewise` — return per-variable OOB error if `TRUE`.",
    "translatedContent": "* `parallelize` — `\"no\"`, `\"variables\"`, या `\"forests\"`।"
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "x/C/C2MD6K7W7Cp5s5DIiQBsRT83DANaxEANKoCNkaQ=",
    "originContent": "* `parallelize` — `\"no\"`, `\"variables\"`, or `\"forests\"`.",
    "translatedContent": "* `num.threads` — `ranger` के लिए थ्रेड्स (`randomForest` द्वारा अनदेखा किया जाता है)।"
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "NYCEfXqJJXx1d/2vgUP2s1LiI+qpuXGGLnmHc6RSKMs=",
    "originContent": "* `num.threads` — threads for `ranger` (ignored by `randomForest`).",
    "translatedContent": "* `backend` — `\"ranger\"` (डिफ़ॉल्ट) या `\"randomForest\"`।"
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "3n5wgY/huM3VqhDC8qPgOm1xOWv7+6ssDPFs3nMEAYQ=",
    "originContent": "* `backend` — `\"ranger\"` (default) or `\"randomForest\"`.",
    "translatedContent": "* `xtrue` — **बेंचमार्किंग** के लिए वैकल्पिक पूर्ण डेटा (यह `$error` जोड़ता है)।"
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "15kjxz+KCZvxXQqu1nDj9D/P+oeYF4KiXSAxw2ib+X0=",
    "originContent": "* `xtrue` — optional complete data for **benchmarking** (adds `$error`).",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "`backend = \"ranger\"` के लिए कुछ आर्ग्युमेंट मैपिंग्स:"
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "8eHZGhV5reKNX4PrSdrLeI3bNZ2QjSjPwJ/khknoarI=",
    "originContent": "Some argument mappings for `backend = \"ranger\"`:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 143,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "* `ntree → num.trees`"
  },
  {
    "row": 144,
    "rowsha": "XZxxKzhzFLTbkPaScYbenFiu7qNU5TuCTlLwDkCT+J4=",
    "originContent": "* `ntree → num.trees`",
    "translatedContent": "* `nodesize → min.bucket` (रेग्रेशन/क्लासिफिकेशन के लिए अलग-अलग; डिफ़ॉल्ट `c(5,1)`)"
  },
  {
    "row": 145,
    "rowsha": "W8BQ6LHOfWSl1tblcECe6wLh058Di8APEnoe1+xnUgU=",
    "originContent": "* `nodesize → min.bucket` (separately for regression/classification; default `c(5,1)`)",
    "translatedContent": "* `sampsize` (गिनती) → `sample.fraction` (फ्रैक्शंस; ओवरऑल या प्रति-क्लास)"
  },
  {
    "row": 146,
    "rowsha": "MnEibNsloH+jw3VJ/LHRIDrthN29xl+mNrFUEVSuSi4=",
    "originContent": "* `sampsize` (counts) → `sample.fraction` (fractions; overall or per-class)",
    "translatedContent": "* `classwt → class.weights`"
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
    "rowsha": "lQRv5KOROSG97lpXqJRwg/nR16XsT0Jl+KHFUsvSQ0Q=",
    "originContent": "* `classwt → class.weights`",
    "translatedContent": "* `cutoff` को **probability forests** बनाकर और पोस्ट-थ्रेशोल्डिंग द्वारा संभाला जाता है"
  },
  {
    "row": 148,
    "rowsha": "PwhZcqxDAt1DdYit8WOmcKTA+Bzo+IsqgorRkwR/rgk=",
    "originContent": "* `cutoff` handled by fitting **probability forests** and post-thresholding",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 149,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### यूटिलिटीज"
  },
  {
    "row": 150,
    "rowsha": "CMj8oo3YwE9CF+KpT+zwXU1SGJkScqoB44lhh7CgcFI=",
    "originContent": "### Utilities",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 151,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "* `mixError(ximp, xmis, xtrue)` — सही मिसिंग एंट्रीज़ पर **NRMSE** (न्यूमेरिक) और **PFC** (फैक्टर) की गणना करता है।"
  },
  {
    "row": 152,
    "rowsha": "sJkX+NDYqM+pCSrUu1fsZp+5j0AfDtIlqm0DpQaDmic=",
    "originContent": "* `mixError(ximp, xmis, xtrue)` — computes **NRMSE** (numeric) and **PFC** (factor) over true missing entries.",
    "translatedContent": "* `nrmse(ximp, xmis, xtrue)` — केवल कंटीन्युअस डेटा के लिए NRMSE।"
  },
  {
    "row": 153,
    "rowsha": "h1bhpyrQ69gOGL+2vtw9ogVcwSWuK4QceTv2KW3mitQ=",
    "originContent": "* `nrmse(ximp, xmis, xtrue)` — NRMSE for continuous-only data.",
    "translatedContent": "* `prodNA(x, noNA = 0.1)` — डेटा फ्रेम में MCAR मिसिंगनेस डालता है।"
  },
  {
    "row": 154,
    "rowsha": "0+WK6DUL5rR0sDRXzaQTEocSMjB9KUv7heaGANi0FW8=",
    "originContent": "* `prodNA(x, noNA = 0.1)` — injects MCAR missingness into a data frame.",
    "translatedContent": "* `varClass(x)` — प्रति कॉलम `\"numeric\"`/`\"factor\"` लौटाता है।"
  },
  {
    "row": 155,
    "rowsha": "5LirCzw8IM4eGe48Gs8YxhEarDMCkmG3FJX/ggXQAs0=",
    "originContent": "* `varClass(x)` — returns `\"numeric\"`/`\"factor\"` per column.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 156,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
